    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true time capsule: this vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, meticulously preserved to satisfy the most discerning collector. The exterior paint retains its original factory deep-gloss luster, entirely free of swirls, rock chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is laser-straight with perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple with zero creasing, the carpets are pristine, and every switchgear operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history and having been stored in a climate-controlled environment since day one. This is not just a used car; it is a museum-quality example that has never seen rain or snow. If you are looking for the finest specimen on the market, your search ends here.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
